high_descs: Move to stand at the counter between the stove and sink.
Pick up the sharp knife from the counter.
Use the knife to slice the tomato on the counter.
Turn to face the sink while carrying the knife.
Place the knife on the narrow strip of counter in front of the sink.
Turn back to face the tomato on the counter.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the counter.
Turn and carry the tomato to the sink.
Place the tomato slice in the sink, turn on the water, and remove once washed.
Carry the tomato slice to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the tomato slice on the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed slice of tomato in the fridge.

high_descs: turn right, go around center counter to counter to the right of stove
pick up knife to the right of round pot
slice tomato on counter behind round pot and in front of apple
turn right to face the sink
place knife with handle on edge of sink and blade over the sink
turn left to face counter with round pot
pick up tomato slice in between round pot and apple
turn to the right and face sink
place tomato slice to the left of bowl in sink
turn on water, pick up tomato slice from sink
go to refrigerator to the right, open refrigerator, place tomato slice on top shelf of refrigerator, close refrigerator
anns.task_desc: Place washed tomato slice on top shelf of refrigerator

high_descs: Turn to the right, walk around the counter, go to the sink.
Pick up the knife to the right of the pot.
Slice the tomato closest to the pot.
Turn to the right.
Put the knife on the counter in front of the sink.
Turn to the left.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn to the sink.
Wash the tomato slice in the sink, pick the tomato slice back up.
Turn to the right, walk to the fridge.
Put the tomato slice in the fridge on the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put the clean slice of tomato in the fridge.
